# Privacy Policy for Genesis Journey

**Last updated:** March 16, 2026

Genesis Journey (“we,” “our,” or “us”) respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how Genesis Journey handles information when you use our game.

Genesis Journey is a faith-driven Bible adventure game designed to provide an interactive and enjoyable gameplay experience centered on biblical learning and storytelling.

## 1. Information We Collect

At this time, Genesis Journey is designed to collect **little to no personal information directly** from players.

Depending on how the game is built and distributed, we may process limited information such as:

- Basic device or technical information needed for the app to run properly
- Local saved game data stored on your device
- App store–provided data related to downloads, installs, or crash reporting
- Information you voluntarily provide if you contact us for support

We do **not** intentionally collect sensitive personal information unless it is clearly necessary for a feature you choose to use.

## 2. Local Device Storage

Genesis Journey may save certain gameplay data locally on your device, such as:

- Player progress
- Settings and preferences
- Selected character or journey data
- Game achievements or completion markers

This information is generally stored on your device to allow the game to function properly and help you continue where you left off.

## 3. How We Use Information

Any information processed by Genesis Journey is used only to:

- Operate the game
- Save gameplay progress
- Improve performance and stability
- Respond to support requests
- Maintain security and prevent misuse

We do not sell your personal information.

## 4. Third-Party Services

Depending on the version of the app, Genesis Journey may rely on third-party platforms or services such as:

- Google Play
- Apple App Store
- Device operating system services
- Crash reporting or analytics tools, if added in the future

These third parties may collect data according to their own privacy policies and platform rules. If third-party analytics, advertising, cloud saves, or account systems are added later, this Privacy Policy will be updated accordingly.

## 5. Children’s Privacy

Genesis Journey is intended to be a faith-based educational and entertainment experience for a broad audience. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children in violation of applicable law.

If you are a parent or guardian and believe a child has provided personal information through the game, please contact us so we can review and address the issue.

## 6. Data Sharing

We do not sell, rent, or trade personal information.

We may share limited information only when necessary to:

- Operate or maintain the game
- Comply with legal obligations
- Protect the rights, safety, and security of users, the game, or others
- Work with service providers who help support app functionality

## 7. Data Retention

If gameplay data is stored locally on your device, it may remain there until you delete the app or clear the app’s storage.

If you contact us directly, we may retain your message long enough to respond to you, keep appropriate business records, or comply with legal obligations.

## 8. Your Choices

You may be able to control certain data practices by:

- Deleting the app
- Clearing app storage on your device
- Adjusting device permissions in your phone or tablet settings
- Choosing whether to contact us or provide support information

If future versions of Genesis Journey include accounts, cloud saves, or analytics controls, we will describe those choices here.

## 9. Security

We take reasonable steps to protect information associated with Genesis Journey. However, no method of electronic storage or transmission is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

## 10. International Users

If Genesis Journey is downloaded or used outside the United States, your information may be processed in accordance with applicable laws in your region and the laws of the jurisdictions in which our services operate.

## 11. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. If we make material changes, we will update the “Last updated” date above and, where appropriate, provide additional notice in the app or store listing.

